      "rationale": "Grid convergence study was performed at a single operating point (3 L/min, 3000 RPM) using three mesh levels (1.2M, 3.8M, 9.6M cells). GCI for the hemolysis index at this point was 8.3%, exceeding the 5% acceptance threshold. The study was not repeated at the remaining four operating points due to computational resource constraints. Discretization error cannot be confirmed below the required threshold across the full operating envelope. Required level 2 was not achieved; achieved level assessed at 1."
    },
