      "rationale": "CFD predictions of the normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) were compared against FDA experimental measurements. Agreement within ±15% was achieved at 4 of 5 operating points; the fifth point showed 18% deviation attributed to transitional flow effects. Overall comparison supports required level 2."
